# 2026-04-06 14:06:15.780002
+Make sure you try to determine if this is an observation of something describing work being done by a contractor or if the user specifically talks about a vendor, supplier or contractor doing something then set the contractor toggle to yes. By default, the during working hours should be yes, unless it was an activity normally happening over a weekend or the user specificaly said this was outside of working hours. 

# 2026-04-06 14:08:15.964446
+The default project should be the Hatch Global project, but if the user specifically talks about another project or adds the 6 digit number of the other project to the chat, change it to that project. By default, the toggle should select Hatch office, as this is where the user was working from during that day even if the incidient happened after work. Only set it to home office if the user mentions working from home. 

